lead_paragraph: Middlesbrough moved back into the automatic promotion places with a 3-2 win at Queens Park Rangers that took them up to second in the English Championship on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Middlesbrough Boost Promotion Push With 3-2 Win at QPR
